item.title: About
item.description: Interests I am interested in recording, understanding and simulating the natural world around us. I explore these interests through: Photography: A means for me to record and comprehend natural phenomena, while also delving into the nuances of camera technology. I am intrigued by the challenges that come with exploring the limits of consumer-level budget cameras. Outdoor adventures: I enjoy hiking and biking. I feel most alive after overcoming difficult physical challenges and being rewarded with a breathtaking view.
